overview: The user initiated a task to enhance a sleep questionnaire application
  by integrating a database and an admin dashboard. After reviewing the existing
  codebase and clarifying requirements for authentication complexity and
  demographic data, the agent developed a comprehensive plan. This plan involved
  updating the application's demographic data structure, defining a new
   model in Prisma for storing survey results, and
  creating API endpoints to manage these responses, including a CSV export
  feature. A simple, password-based authentication system was also implemented
  to secure the future admin dashboard. The agent successfully completed the
  updates to demographics, the Prisma schema, the authentication helpers and
  system, and the API routes for responses and CSV export, laying a solid
  foundation for the admin dashboard.
